These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, sprite, hot-chocolate, milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, musical, romance, thriller, adventure
There are 5 different nationalities: french, colombian, indonesian, polish, pakistani
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, ferret, dog, mouse
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the french is on the left of the indonesian##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the person drinking milk is between the colombian and the person watching adventure movies##2
12. the polish is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
13. the pakistani is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea        | cola | milk     | sprite   | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | musical      | thriller | adventure   | horror    |
| Nationality   | polish  | colombian     | french | indonesian | pakistani  |
| Pet           | frog | ferret      | mouse     | dog   | goldfish     |

