.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, cooking, photography, fishing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, ambient, trance, reggae, hip-hop
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, italian, australian, nigerian, colombian
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, ship, motorbike, boat
 1. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the italian##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the brazilian and the fan of hip-hop##2
 6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 8. the australian is the fan of reggae##1
 9. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
11. the australian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | photography | board-games | fishing    | drawing  | cooking    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | ambient       | trance      | blues | reggae        |
| Nationality   | colombian   | italian     | brazilian    | nigerian  | australian     |
| Transport     | ship    | jet-ski | boat | motorbike | train |

