.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: woodworking, hiking, cooking, camping, chess
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, drama, time-travel, epic, comedy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, disco, d&b, country, hip-hop
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, snowboarding, biathlon, sailing, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is the fan of disco##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | woodworking | chess     | cooking   | hiking   | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | drama | zombie | epic | time-travel        |
