.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: pear, nectarine, raspberry, apple, pineapple
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, video-games, drawing, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, d&b, punk, gospel, r&b
There are 5 different nationalities: turkish, german, nigerian, chinese, american
 1. the german is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 4. the american is between the fan of gospel and the person eating apple##2
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the right of the nigerian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is the fan of d&b##1
 9. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
10. the fan of gospel is the turkish##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the turkish is on the right of the fan of punk##1
13. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | pineapple  | raspberry     | apple   | nectarine     | pear |
| Hobby         | writing | dancing    | drawing  | sudoku | video-games   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | pop    | r&b     | punk     | gospel    |
| Nationality   | german    | nigerian | chinese | american | turkish   |

