.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, water, fanta, soy-milk
There 5 different types of food: plum, cabbage, spinach, eggplant, potato
The people have 5 different jobs:  nurse, software-developer, musician, teacher, videographer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, handball, surfing, basketball, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the nurse##1
 2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the person drinking water is between the person who's sport is handball and the person eating plum##2
 5. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the software-developer##1
 8. the videographer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the nurse##1
11. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
12. the teacher is on the left of the nurse##1
13. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | fanta       | soy-milk       | tea   | water      | cola    |
| Food       | potato | eggplant        | plum       | spinach       | cabbage |
| Job        | videographer     | software-developer        | teacher | nurse        | musician  |
| Sport      | basketball | surfing | swimming      | rugby | handball  |

