 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's sport is cycling##2
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the russian##1
 8. the thai is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the dutch##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
11. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's sport is cycling##2
12. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the canadian##1
13. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
