 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person driving the car##1
 4. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the australian##2
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
 7. the spanish is on the right of the pakistani##1
 8. the german is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the cat is the spanish##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
11. the owner of the cat is on the right of the pakistani##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
