 3. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | tea       | hot-chocolate    | fanta | water  | almond-milk        |
| Hobby       | skydiving | cooking | dancing  | puzzles | magic-tricks    |
| Sport       | cycling        | badminton   | lacrosse  | surfing   | volleyball |
| Transport   | bus       | skateboard      | bike      | ship | scooter  |

