.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, tea
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, doctor, manager, musician, writer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, family, martial-arts, comedy, zombie
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, reggae, punk, r&b, dubstep
 1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 2. the musician is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the manager##2
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the musician##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person watching western movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the writer and the fan of reggae##2
 7. the fan of r&b is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of punk##1
 9. the fan of techno is on the left of the writer##1
10. the police-officer is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the manager is the person watching family movies##1
12. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

