The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, soul, metal, folk, funk
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, pakistani, turkish, british, colombian
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is between the british and the fan of funk##2
 3. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of hip-hop##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is between the colombian and the fan of metal##2
 6. the colombian is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of folk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is funk-climbing is the fan of soul##1
 9. the dutch is the fan of soul##1
10. the person who's hobby is funk-climbing is on the right of the turkish##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
12. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
